question: A student prepared a presentation to show how water changes the surface of Earth. Which presentation would best demonstrate how water changes the surface of Earth?
candidate_answers: (A) a diagram of a river food web (B) a graph of the amount of rainfall on a lake (C) a picture of fog covering a mountain valley (D) a model of a stream flowing down a hillside
answer: a model of a stream flowing down a hillside
label: D
